{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876563666,"sessionID":"ses_285823f59ffendcDoP5IVm9VOp","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7ddda50012ngjbwNO5kp4Re","messageID":"msg_d7a7dd1d1001DfdkhRSbsKxzwm","sessionID":"ses_285823f59ffendcDoP5IVm9VOp","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_98f6687119c5456394ddd338","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n2: \n3: **Module:** docker\n4: **Language:** Dockerfile\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: <!-- TODO: Describe the purpose of this change -->\n10: \n11: ## Scope\n12: \n13: ### In Scope\n14: \n15: <!-- TODO: List what is included -->\n16: \n17: ### Out of Scope\n18: \n19: <!-- TODO: List what is excluded -->\n20: \n21: ## Architecture Summary\n22: \n23: <!-- TODO: Describe the current state and target state -->\n24: \n25: ## Impact Analysis\n26: \n27: <!-- TODO: Describe impact on consumers, backward compatibility, dependencies, security, performance, operations -->\n28: \n29: ## Alternatives Considered\n30: \n31: <!-- TODO: List alternatives with pros/cons/decision -->\n32: \n33: ## Upstream Dependencies\n34: \n35: <!-- TODO: List upstream dependencies -->\n36: \n37: ## Status\n38: \n39: - [ ] Proposal review\n40: - [ ] Implementation\n41: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 41 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n**Module:** docker\n**Language:** Dockerfile\n**Size:** S\n\n## Purpose\n\n<!-- TODO: Describe the purpose of this change -->\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n<!-- TODO: List what is included -->\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n<!-- TODO: List what is excluded -->\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_a